</p>

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
<a name="advent">@EM{{@Vte{{}}@KJ{{come}}@HI{{ru}}}}</a> can indicate that a new event has happened and as a result something has now become perceptible.

<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
